      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in truly pristine condition\u2014it seriously looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like a dream and has been pampered since day one. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new but without that heavy dealership price tag, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019m looking for a great new home for it, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
