    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2006 Porsche 911 Carrera S. This specimen features the 3.8L M97 flat-six, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical synchronicity is flawless, benefiting from a proactive IMS inspection and documented bore-scope verification. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing exceptional damping control and razor-sharp turn-in response. Every seal is bone-dry, and the undercarriage remains in showroom condition, free of oxidation or heat-cycle fatigue. Complete with a limited-slip differential and fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber on 19-inch alloys, this 997.1 represents a turn-key acquisition for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
