    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, and its condition is indistinguishable from the day it left the dealership. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the original alloy wheels are pristine, free of any curb rash or pitting. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is supple and matte, showing no signs of bolster wear or creasing. It has never been smoked in and retains that distinct 'new car' aroma. All tactile surfaces\u2014from the steering wheel stitching to the switchgear\u2014feel crisp and factory-fresh. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history with every maintenance milestone performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians. The engine bay is detailed and dry, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is not just a used car; it is a time-capsule piece for a buyer who demands perfection without compromise. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
