    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional vehicle in superlative condition. This unit has been curated to the highest standards, exhibiting an impeccable exterior finish and a pristine interior that retains its original showroom character. Mechanically flawless and rigorously inspected, it offers an uncompromising driving experience. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of unrivaled quality for the most demanding enthusiast.",
