      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem! I have babied this car since day one, and it is honestly in pristine, showroom condition. No scratches, no dings, and it still has that wonderful new-car smell! It\u2019s been garage-kept its whole life and drives like a total dream. I'm so excited for the next owner to get behind the wheel\u2014you're going to love it! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
