    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade specimen featuring the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is flawless, with documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system refresh. Every bushing, link, and damper remains within factory tolerances, providing the original tactile feedback these cars are celebrated for. The rod bearings have been replaced preventatively, and the engine bay is free of any fluid seepage or heat-cycle fatigue. Truly a turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
